summary: THE CONSUMER NOTICED A  CRACK IN THE WINDSHIELD. NO ONE HEARD ANY STONES OR REASONS FOR CRACKING. WENT TO WESPORT HONDA DEALER REPORTED THAT IT LOOKED LIKE CRACK FROM PEBBLE. THE CRACK HAS EXPANDED ACROSS THE  WINDSHIELD. HEARD THAT THERE WAS A RECALL ON HONDA WINDSHIELD ELEMENTS. THE CONSUMER DISCOVERED THERE WAS CLASS ACTION LAWSUIT  PENDING AGAINST  HONDA.
